title: Your Network Equals Your Networth
itunes:title: Your Network Equals Your Networth
description:
Episode 220 - You are the average of the 5 people that you spend the most time with. That means that you literally become who you are always around. In this episode I talk about the categories of people in your life and who you should spend more time with and who you should spend less time with.
